headline: 5 Financial Transaction Stocks to Watch Amid a Booming Digital Era
summary: The Financial Transaction Services industry is aided by the widespread adoption of contactless payments, strong cross-border volumes and pursuit of M&A activities. Companies like V, MA, FI, FIS and GPN are well-positioned to thrive on the back of these favorable trends.
